About_Your_Trip
Formerly named Saigon , Vietnam ’ s Ho_Chi_Minh_City offers visitors a lot to explore , from its French colonial architecture and religious pagodas to bustling markets and modern museums .
Your full - day guided tour of the Mekong_Delta will include a trip down the Tien_River with stops at fishing villages and the islands of Dragon , Unicorn , Tortoise and Phoenix . Other highlights include a trek through coconut plantations and a rowboat to Thoi_Son_Island , where , while refreshing yourself with tropical fruit and honey tea , you ’ ll enjoy a live performance of Don_Ca_Tai_Tu , the traditional folk music of southern Vietnam .
What ' s Included
4 days and 3 nights at Le_Méridien_Saigon , 3C Ton_Duc_Thang_Street , District 1 Ho , Chi_Minh_City , Vietnam .
Featuring guest room accommodations with 1 king bed or 2 double beds and complimentary Wi-Fi .
3 breakfasts , 1 lunch and 2 dinners .
Full-day Mekong_Delta tour .
Cruise along Tien_River .
Rowing boat excursion to Thoi_Son_Island .
An_In - destination Support_Specialist will be provided when 20 or more adults book this trip . Their goal is to ensure you have a great DreamTrips experience from landing to liftoff . They host a welcome reception on arrival day , attend scheduled activities throughout the trip , notify the group of itinerary updates and more .
Your trip includes 2 airport transfers :
January 8 , from 9 a . m . to 5 p . m . : From_Tan_Son_Nhat_International_Airport to the hotel .
January 11 , from 8 a . m . to 5 p . m . : From the hotel to Tan_Son_Nhat_International_Airport .
To take advantage of round - trip airport transfers , you must provide your flight information to the DreamTrips Specialist no later than December 24 . These transfers are available only for the airport ( s ) and dates listed above . Click here to give us your flight information . Transfers will not be offered if the flight information is not received by the deadline and transfers at any other time will incur a separate charge . Do not email flight information to the DreamTrips Specialist .
Air transportation is not included . The closest commercial airport is Tan_Son_Nhat_International_Airport ( SGN ) .
For any questions regarding this trip , contact the DreamTrips Specialist at DreamTrips@rovia.com .
Check-in : 3 p . m . Check-out : noon .
Hotel_Details
With its downtown location right along the Saigon_River , Le_Méridien_Saigon makes a scenic and convenient home base for your visit to Ho_Chi_Minh_City .
Guests can relax in comfort and enjoy city or river views from their rooms , or venture to Explore_Spa , the 24-hour fitness center , or the infinity - edge indoor pool to swim laps within view of the Saigon_River ! For dining , the hotel offers the French-influenced Art_Cacao for pastries , Latest_Recipe for modern international and classic Vietnamese dishes , and healthy spa fare at Explore_Bistro & Spa_Café , along with evening cocktails at Latitude .
Boasting dedicated , attentive service and a location close to shopping , dining , local attractions and entertainment , Le_Méridien_Saigon is sure to impress .
Le_Méridien_Saigon
3C Ton_Duc_Thang_Street
District 1 , Ho_Chi_Minh_City , Vietnam
